The paper focuses on utilizing neural language modeling approaches for embedding tabular data into vector spaces and using these embeddings for table-related tasks such as row population, column population, and table retrieval. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Database (cs.DB), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
